{"tid":1598482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【9.28】民陣：【反抗威權 迎接黎明】","createTime":"2019-09-27T13:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T07:11:36.000Z","uid":212626,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0ccd2d5e4f1e0ac315d368f19949c37a81e87d47","tid":1598482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"#香港人Assemble！聽日！All in添馬公園！<br />\n<br />\n反抗威權 迎接黎明<br />\n2019年9月28日<br />\n晚上7時至9時<br />\n添馬公園集會<br />\n<br />\n#大家記得留意集會時間<br />\n#係夜晚7至9<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#人民歸來 #WeAreBack<br />\n#香港人Assemble<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7A0n3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7A0n3s.jpg&h=68f2f50d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2492346777479365/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2492346777479365%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=0f34fd77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2492346777479365/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"17780765d9bf5c048c42a7fb46d423cfb43f676a","tid":1598482,"uid":240077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:05:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05eea78e0e5bb9a6d3bec41ab91671a4113484e","tid":1598482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbab23f02c7fc32ebc77f789171d6d90491bcd9e","tid":1598482,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔知我有無聽錯，十一聖上閱兵期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">假如同一時間有遊行，係絕對唔會有清場行動。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令聖上即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。但之前上面會嚇窒唔俾大家出，但如果出咗佢都耐你唔何。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span>"},{"pid":"75e0ab554a5a9231c6b40fde6fe2ead48e148a2b","tid":1598482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70b7cd94b051653bd65512ef68e3e7047b4e5da","tid":1598482,"uid":201816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef582122200c12a808d716e3abf89f918bb4376","tid":1598482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b096165cc709aa52fb8a39d1546e06e9d7c65437","tid":1598482,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3234405ade9246b50e65f64994f79309a62f77da","tid":1598482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9235fe4a4f982dce54861b1389515ed266306f74","tid":1598482,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:40:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4eba498da0548eb59f583a683f0eca5d7390e77","tid":1598482,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uYhqPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uYhqPQ.jpg&h=9c425